How do you cheat                
on a writing test?              

31:00.860 --> 31:03.360
               Miss parton,     
               front and center.

31:04.497 --> 31:06.463
What did i do?                  

31:06.465 --> 31:10.100
          Not you,              
          sweet stella mae. You.

31:10.102 --> 31:13.604
 Since you were so interested in
 talking during your essay test 

31:13.606 --> 31:16.406
        You can be the first one
        to read yours aloud.    

31:18.377 --> 31:20.077
             Alright, now, dolly

31:20.079 --> 31:23.080
       Please tell us who your  
       favorite famous person is

31:23.082 --> 31:25.249
        And why you admire them?

31:25.251 --> 31:27.985
  Why, that's easy, miss moody. 

31:27.987 --> 31:32.456
 It's miss dolly parton, rising 
 star of the grand ole opry.    

31:32.458 --> 31:33.590
            [scoffs]            

31:33.592 --> 31:35.592
    She was born                
    on a cold winter's night    

31:35.594 --> 31:37.561
  In locust ridge, tennessee.   

31:37.563 --> 31:39.296
She was singing                 
before she could talk.          

31:39.298 --> 31:43.000
 Doc thomas swore she came out  
 screaming in the key of "e."   

31:43.002 --> 31:45.269
          Yeah, i bet.          

31:45.271 --> 31:48.972
  Hey, this is my paper,        
